'''''Veve'''''  ni film y'ikinamico yo muri [[Kenya]] 2014 iyobowe na Simon Mukali. VEVE ni co-production of One Fine Day Films na Ginger Ink.<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20141022014347/http://www.standardmedia.co.ke/?articleID=2000133975&story_title=Kenya-veve-depicts-kenya-s-political-fast-lane "‘Veve’ depicts Kenya’s political fast lane", ''Standard Digital News'']</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Amos, umwe mu bagize Inteko ishinga amategeko w’ibanze, arashaka kuba guverineri wa Maua mu matora ari imbere mu gihe yagura inyungu z’ubucuruzi. Ni umutanga wingenzi kubohereza ibicuruzwa hanze, Wadu, umucuruzi uzi ubwenge, utegeka umugabane munini wubucuruzi. Nyuma y'ikiganiro numucungamari we winyuma, Amos abona umwanya wo kuzamura umubano we w'akazi na Wadu no kubona imigabane minini mubucuruzi. Yasangiye umugambi we n’umugabo we w’iburyo witwa Sammy, wagize uruhare runini mu kubaka imbaraga za Amosi, amukorera imirimo yanduye. Ariko Sammy yifuza imirimo nk'iyi iragabanuka. Aracyafite agahinda k'urupfu rw'umugore we nubwo hashize imyaka mike, Sammy arwana urugamba rwo guhuza umubyeyi n'umuhungu we wigometse, uhumeka kole.

